Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(850,850)\pos(160,380)\fnSimSun\fs30}第二话 潜航极限
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.68,0:00:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跃迁立场？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.06,0:00:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.89,0:00:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聋了吗 开始炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.73,0:00:21.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敌舰的瞄准镭射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.47,0:00:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本舰舰尾已被锁定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.03,0:00:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大输出功率 起航准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.16,0:00:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴鲁丹诺斯 起航
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向下45度 急速潜航
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.32,0:01:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿度亚的船 居然可以潜沙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受强脉冲磁场的影响 产生了电磁干扰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去目标踪影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止给电子室供应等离子体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:52.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测班迅速用肉眼确认情况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为沙尘的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可见光和远红外线都难以捕捉到敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.15,0:03:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方沙地有内聚力崩溃反应
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是拟似相变立场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,QTF吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 第三类戒备
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对潜舰模式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.45,0:03:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声纳员 展开声纳阵列
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在LS界面相完全沉没之前抓住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声纳阵列 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阵列启动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不只是潜沙那么简单呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深度300 界面相潜行中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前 船内的损坏情况无异常
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有被追踪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三艘舰船的锅炉音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从左舷后方接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.03,0:04:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然在他们眼前消失所以慌了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.21,0:04:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俩舷的锅炉熄火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长 他们的锅炉音...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是想拖住我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来敌人多半是懂沙战的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在垂钓等我们上钩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰 进入第四就绪状态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解 主锅炉 俩舷减速
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俩舷微速
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:03.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锅炉噪音降至60分贝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2号“猎犬”没能确认目标船只的声纹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扩大1和3号“猎犬”的搜索范围
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是摒起气息藏起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:19.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在强化榴弹上装上延迟信管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.58,0:05:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向目标船只的潜航地点前方1000米处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以散布角度5度的散点爆炸方式发射
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有动静了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是发射音 他们打过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 准备迎接冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸弹的位置别听错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 萨姆 你也来帮帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小猫咪 乖乖呆着别动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸地点 前方1000米
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然他们只是在瞎蒙而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢 这不是攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过刚才的爆炸 他们确认了我们的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 30方向 两舷微速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两舷微速前进
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到目标回音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示到1号屏幕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在干扰纹波上观测到内聚力崩溃的群延时特性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然目标展开了拟似相变立场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LS界面相的半径呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约120米
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想像中的要大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,界面相移动了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30方向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声纹消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用非线性预测滤波器继续追踪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.96,0:07:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给垂直发射系统装上沙锚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要用沙锚进行攻击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于沙中的敌人 激光枪没有丝毫作用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那样的话玛雅大人她...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前最重要的是把目标留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我负全责
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:47.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装填沙锚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1357号垂直发射系统 装填锚杆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.81,0:07:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹道瞄准 锁定LS界面相的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准 修正误差
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.38,0:08:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙锚能量注入完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时可以发射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙锚 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰的发射音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4发 6发 越来越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是发射深沙炸弹了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 如果是深沙炸弹 撞击声会更小一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,播放发射音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.02,0:08:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射音 播放中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俩舷全速 右满舵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.13,0:09:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要冲进岩礁地带了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管 继续前进
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动主动声纳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 上面那些人...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.63,0:09:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题 岩礁是很好的掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动主动声纳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脉冲？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11点方向传来脉冲的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是主动声纳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出音源的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回音？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右舷30度 钻到3号和5号的中间去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷两倍速 右舷30度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.91,0:09:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫 在干着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右舷45度 绕到5号那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右舷45度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用多普勒差分滤波器 把那艘船给我挖出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过5号了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12点方向 不规则岩礁6号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.14,0:10:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俩舷停止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锅炉 全力急停
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:32.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准 最终调整
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.79,0:10:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将数据传送到沙锚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙锚 突入沙底
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上方有冲击音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙锚的回音 捕捉到未知的冲击波
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.93,0:11:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方区域的粒子穴也已恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.57,0:11:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LS界面相消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是抓到目标了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电磁干涉波有什么反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前还没有观测到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉失败了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.15,0:11:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我想像中还要有两手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上确认损伤状况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎声停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不是什么东西被破坏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 玛雅 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大夫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米梅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快抬她到医务室去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人到底...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是停止了拟似相变立场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.08,0:12:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏在沙中 能让沙锚的威力大打折扣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不展开LS界面相
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩礁就是很好的掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大大降低了被声纳发现的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锅炉室的管道受到一定程度的破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷后方出现裂缝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在亚穆正前往维修
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量子跃迁引擎什么时候再启动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沙里面 很难排热
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.15,0:13:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰内的温度 以及对舰艇的压力 都...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.38,0:13:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们应该知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是在潜沙那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来敌人很有头脑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长 这样下去撑不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群家伙继续坐在那里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击吧 还能勉强把鱼雷从这里发射到地面去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘记了我们还没来得及取得补给吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射管里面只剩下两枚鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使全部命中 敌人还有一艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 这样妥当吗 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅大人就在敌舰上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脉搏很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米梅 注射3号药水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我拿水来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.23,0:14:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:03.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船内温度超过了45度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰内的温度即将超过界限
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.35,0:15:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是那样 玛雅大人...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 会撑不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船内温度 48度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船内温度 即将超过50度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船...船长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全舰 微速后退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就此回航
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.87,0:16:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量子跃迁引擎 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上浮至潜望镜深度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:16:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢复了恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一群没耐性的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.18,0:18:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你什么都没干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛嚷得那么大声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫什么都没干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.48,0:18:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又扇扇子 又端水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我觉得这纯粹是在碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没碍事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,475)\fnSimSun\fad(840,0)\fs25}Theseus总部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:18:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下等人拿度亚的沙贼船 居然能潜沙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.19,0:19:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.32,0:19:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是下属小看了拿度亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.91,0:19:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群可恶的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是太过纵容他们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.22,0:19:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要给点苦头他们吃才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.60,0:19:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛雅大人为何想从我们的保护之下逃跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她身处的时间和空间都跟我们不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人能了解她的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当她的保姆实在是当腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此 对我们来说 她是必不可缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.98,0:19:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 属下定会将她带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没什么时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸一下新鲜空气 心情也会开朗一点的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我有好东西 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.40,0:20:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白娜丝 我进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还纳闷着今天是个什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:20:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟平时没什么两样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.46,0:21:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆带回来那个女孩子的病历
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.66,0:21:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治疗的时候有点在意 就去查了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.99,0:21:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可不是一般人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.35,0:23:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Theseus那些家伙 为什么盯上我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.72,0:23:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传言萨姆带回来的那个女孩子会带来厄运
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.83,0:23:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这话 小心萨姆跑来揍你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.26,0:23:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对面已经打起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.89,0:23:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也插一脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.20,0:23:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,300)\fnSimSun\fs30}第三话 “千年的迷惑”
